        <item>
            <title>平治全新智能纯电 EQA 及 EQB 到港，精致设计风格、全新设计元素马上睇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/benz-eqa-eqb/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=benz-eqa-eqb</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/benz-eqa-eqb/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 13:05:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EQA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EQB]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[平治]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1256982</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>全新平治轻巧纯电动车 EQA 及 EQB 近日正式到港。这两个最新智能纯电 SUV 从设计上就展现出一贯的精致风格，并融入了多项全新设计元素。以下记者就带大家到香港会场睇睇。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256983" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1441-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1441-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1441.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256984" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1442-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1442-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1442.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1398-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1398-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1398.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>平治纯电动车 EQA 及 EQB 车头的黑色板面鬼面罩配以平治星徽标志，以及镀铬的星徽设计，提升了整体的辨识度。日间行车灯与灯带相连，令车辆在夜间的视觉效果更为突出。全新 EQA 及 EQB 更加强了车头的宽阔感觉，侧面设计以高光黑色装饰点缀雾灯位置，使车身更具现代感。此外，EQA 车型配备 AMG Line 套件，车身同色的轮拱饰边和重新设计的尾灯进一步增强了车辆的运动风格。新推出的两种车身颜色 &#8211; spectral blue 和 high-tech silver，使得车型选择更加丰富。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1430-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1430-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1430.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>进入车内，全新的 EQA 及 EQB 提供了多项现代化的内笼设计，令驾驶者与乘客享有舒适且智能的乘坐体验。配备触控按钮的最新一代方向盘，搭配平治星徽标志及平治图案背光饰板，增添了豪华感。内饰板采用了激光雕刻技术，并具备发光功能，为车厢增添了一抹亮点。标准配备的 10.25 吋中央显示屏，与车内其他高级车款的风格一致，进一步强调了平治电动车的高品质。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1457-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1457-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1457.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256989" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1455-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1455-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1455.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256990" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1461-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1461-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1461.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256991" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1471-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1471-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1471.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在中控台部分，全新的 EQA 及 EQB 均配备了最新的 MBUX 多媒体系统，该系统拥有零层级触控介面，令驾驶者无需滚动介面或使用语音控制即可操作相关功能。此外，车内还配备了选配的 Burmester 环回音响系统，并支援 Dolby Atmos 全景声效，提供身临其境的听觉体验。驾驶者可根据个人喜好，从三种风格（简约、运动、经典）及三种模式（导航、驾驶辅助、服务）中进行选择，并能设置 10 种不同的车厢气氛灯颜色，创造专属的个性化空间。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256992" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1468-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1468-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1468.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256993" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1467-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1467-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1467.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256994" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1470-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1470-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1470.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在科技系统方面，全新的 EQA 及 EQB 提供了多达四种 Sound Experiences，这些声效可透过中央显示屏选择或关闭，为驾驶者及乘客带来不同的听觉体验。当驾驶者靠近并进入车厢时，车辆会发出迎接的声效，离开时亦会伴随特定的 Aura 声效。行驶时的声效能够随著油门踏板位置、车速等变化，带来更具互动性的驾驶体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256995" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1484-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1484-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1484.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1465-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1465-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1465.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256997" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1448-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1448-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1448.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在安全性方面，EQA 和 EQB 均配备了升级的驾驶辅助系统和感应技术。全新的 mono-multipurpose 摄像机和倒车摄像机能够提供更准确的视野，而主动式车道保持辅助系统则能提供更舒适的转向干预。此外，车辆还配备了 360°泊车镜头，驾驶者可以更直观快捷地完成泊车操作，无论是在平行停车位还是垂直停车位中，都能轻松泊车。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256998" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1453-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1453-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1453.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1450-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1450-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1450.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1446-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1446-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1446.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>最后，行车安全方面，全新 EQA 和 EQB 均具备先进的热管理系统，并标准配备热泵。这不仅提升了车内的舒适性，还大幅降低了电池电量的消耗，进而延长了车辆的续航距离。EQA 车型的续航距离最高可达 569 公里（根据 WLTP 标准），而 EQB 则提供类似的性能表现。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024081890026-694x443.png" alt="" width="694" height="443" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024081890026-694x443.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024081890026.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/13/benz-level-4-auto-drive-in-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">平治获批北京 Lv4 自动驾驶测试　测试车设冗余系统 + 无需人类随时接管</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/09/mercedes-benz-eqs-facelift-spy-photos/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Facelift 版 2025 年推出，平治 EQS 新车谍照曝光</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/mercedes-benz-seized-over-1-6-mil-counterfeit-parts-in-2023/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">平治截获逾 160 万件伪冒零件，全球各地突击检查 740 次</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/benz-eqa-eqb/life-tech/auto/">平治全新智能纯电 EQA 及 EQB 到港，精致设计风格、全新设计元素马上睇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
