            <title>Windows 放宽 FAT32 格式化限制　最大容量从 32GB 提升至 2TB</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/windows-%e6%94%be%e5%af%ac-fat32-%e6%a0%bc%e5%bc%8f%e5%8c%96%e9%99%90%e5%88%b6%e3%80%80%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%a7%e5%ae%b9%e9%87%8f%e5%be%9e-32gb-%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b3-2tb/software/windows-11/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=windows-%25e6%2594%25be%25e5%25af%25ac-fat32-%25e6%25a0%25bc%25e5%25bc%258f%25e5%258c%2596%25e9%2599%2590%25e5%2588%25b6%25e3%2580%2580%25e6%259c%2580%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25ae%25b9%25e9%2587%258f%25e5%25be%259e-32gb-%25e6%258f%2590%25e5%258d%2587%25e8%2587%25b3-2tb</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/windows-%e6%94%be%e5%af%ac-fat32-%e6%a0%bc%e5%bc%8f%e5%8c%96%e9%99%90%e5%88%b6%e3%80%80%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%a7%e5%ae%b9%e9%87%8f%e5%be%9e-32gb-%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b3-2tb/software/windows-11/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 13:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Windows 11]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[FAT32]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1256921</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>一直以来 Windows 在进行硬碟格式化的时候，选择 FAT32 时会限制容量最大只可以到 32GB，虽然其实 FAT32 理论容量远不只如此，但一直未有修改，直到最近才终于放宽限制。<br /><span id="more-1256921"></span></p><p>Microsoft 在最新的 Windows 11 Insider Canary Preview Build 中，将命令列下 FAT32 分区的最大容量限制从 32GB 提升至 2TB。目前 FAT32 格式已经不再常用，大多已经改为 NTFS 或者更新的 exFAT，但仍然有一些情况需要使用 FAT32，在现时硬碟和记忆卡容量轻松超越 32GB 的情况下，放宽限制总算是迟到好过无到。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">I wrote this Format dialog back on a rainy Thursday morning at Microsoft in late 1994, I think it was.</p><p>We were porting the bajillion lines of code from the Windows95 user interface over to NT, and Format was just one of those areas where WindowsNT was different enough from… <a href="https://t.co/PbrhQe0n3K">pic.twitter.com/PbrhQe0n3K</a></p><p>&mdash; Dave W Plummer (@davepl1968) <a href="https://twitter.com/davepl1968/status/1772042158046146792?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 24, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>有趣的是，其实在接近 25 年前设定 32GB 的容量限制的工程师本身就认为这是个错误，数值只是随便设定，但这个「错误」一直没有被修改，就连记忆卡的容量普遍超过 32GB 的时代也一直不变。而大部分用家使用的 GUI 介面格式化工具，则仍然以 32GB 为容量上限，未知之后会否有类似的改动。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/16/24221635/microsoft-fat32-partition-size-limit-windows-11">Verge</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/03/recall-on-different-hardware/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Windows 11 AI Recall 功能被破解，不支援硬件也可正常运行</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/22/windows-11-recall/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">英国调查 Windows 11「Recall」功能  AI 记录用家 PC 操作历史涉私隐风险</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/windows-%e6%94%be%e5%af%ac-fat32-%e6%a0%bc%e5%bc%8f%e5%8c%96%e9%99%90%e5%88%b6%e3%80%80%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%a7%e5%ae%b9%e9%87%8f%e5%be%9e-32gb-%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b3-2tb/software/windows-11/">Windows 放宽 FAT32 格式化限制　最大容量从 32GB 提升至 2TB</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
