            <title>全日空 Pokémon 合作拍飞行安全影片，比卡超与一众角色可爱演出</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/pokemon-5/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pokemon-5</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/pokemon-5/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 10:00:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokemon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[全日空]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1256973</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
<p>Pokémon 走进机舱为大人小朋友介绍飞行安全。日本全日空与 Pokémon 合作，推出全新宝可梦主题飞行安全影片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/anasafetyvideofeatur-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/anasafetyvideofeatur-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/anasafetyvideofeatur.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/anasafetyvideofeatur-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/anasafetyvideofeatur-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/anasafetyvideofeatur-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这部影片以生动有趣的方式，介绍飞行安全的基本指引，并借由比卡超与其他受欢迎角色来传递重要安全资讯。影片特别强调在紧急情况下乘客应采取的关键行动，期望能以轻松愉快的方式吸引乘客关注飞行安全。</p><p>全日空的这部双语影片已经在部分航线上播放，包括往返日本、澳洲、东南亚和北美的航班。乘客在登机后，不仅能够欣赏这些可爱的宝可梦角色，还能更清楚地了解安全指引。影片也已经上传至网上，让所有旅客随时可以观看并重温这些有趣的内容。大家可在下面的影片看到他们在影片中的可爱演出。</p><p>全日空希望借由这种创新方式，让乘客在放松之余不忘安全的重要性。航空公司亦提醒乘客，如有任何疑问，应随时向机组人员寻求协助，确保每位乘客在飞行途中都能安全愉快地抵达目的地。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_96801"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SAolvci7SeA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SAolvci7SeA">YouTube</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/pokemon-5/life-tech/">全日空 Pokémon 合作拍飞行安全影片，比卡超与一众角色可爱演出</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
